tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Wait time,
review: Both Dr. Mr & Mrs Rane are very professional and friendly. They don’t go for the pockets of the patient rather explain them in detail about any dental issue and leave the patient to take a call. I have been visiting them since 2013 and have recommended to many. The aura of their clinic is something to talk about and it is hygienic and clean. Would recommend many more to go to them.

I had severe pain in my upper right side molar and I could not sleep because of it, so I came to Dr Rane. He explained me the entire procedure for my aching tooth very patiently and performed the root canal treatment for my tooth. Now my pain is history and I can chew my food better. I really appreciate drs patience as I can't see and hear, still he took efforts to make me understand the entire process. Thank you Dr.

I was bit reluctant when I visited doctor for the first time through a reference. But, it hardly took any time to be comfortable during the treatment. Dr. Rane is an amazing personality and equally a good professional with excellent knowledge in his field. 

I strongly recommend Dr. Rane for dental treatment as I would prefer to leave with tooth pain, if Dr. Rane is not available for couple of days, instead of visiting any other doctor.

10/10 for the Doctor and helping staff, right from start to end.
Very hard to find such.
Highly recommended !!

review:
Amazing Dr...my 4 year old was very comfortable with the Dr an absolute tear free process...in fact, I was a little away and the process was well managed by Dr
Million thanks ☺️

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: Solved problem immediately. I always blindly go to dr prasad and both doctors are just mindblowing expert
Pleasant experience.Courteous employeesThe doctor was explaining each and every part of the procedure,which was satisfying
It was a good experience. The doctor is very knowledgeable. Appropriate analysis of the case was done and suitable treatment was recommended. I would definitely recommend to anyone.
It was pleasant..not the usual tense ambience of a dentist chamber. The doctor was very friendly and so were the staff. I felt safe in expert hands......
Brilliant.would recommend anyone to come to Dr.Rane for a wonderful and comfortable experience along with high quality expertise.
